Quit gawking at Rukako's body.

224
00:15:07,417 --> 00:15:08,875
I'm not!

225
00:15:08,875 --> 00:15:11,125
Another indecent development!

226
00:15:11,125 --> 00:15:14,292
What do you think? Does this
costume look nice on Ruka-<i>kun</i>?

227
00:15:14,292 --> 00:15:17,000
Y-Yes! It's very cute!

228
00:15:17,000 --> 00:15:19,750
C-Cute...? That's not...

229
00:15:19,750 --> 00:15:22,833
Let's try on some other clothes!

230
00:15:22,833 --> 00:15:24,125
Wait...

231
00:15:24,125 --> 00:15:30,083
I came by today because
I have a favor to ask.

232
00:15:30,083 --> 00:15:33,083
You didn't come to try on my costumes?

233
00:15:33,083 --> 00:15:38,292
Th-That's what I kept trying to say,
but you wouldn't hear me out.

234
00:15:38,292 --> 00:15:40,333
Sorry! I was just so
happy that I couldn't help it...

235
00:15:40,333 --> 00:15:42,292
So, what is this request of yours?

236
00:15:42,292 --> 00:15:44,458
Umm, well, you see...

237
00:15:46,208 --> 00:15:49,542
I want to send a message to the past too!

238
00:15:50,125 --> 00:15:51,750
Yesterday...

239
00:15:53,333 --> 00:15:57,042
I brought a present to make up
for messing up the Loto 6 ticket,

240
00:15:57,042 --> 00:15:59,208
but then...

241
00:15:59,208 --> 00:16:01,083
Wait, did we send another D-mail?!

242
00:16:01,083 --> 00:16:03,750
Huh? Then what does this mean?!

243
00:16:03,750 --> 00:16:05,542
Did we change the past

244
00:16:05,542 --> 00:16:09,875
and cause Kiryu Moeka
to cease to exist entirely...?

245
00:16:09,875 --> 00:16:11,542
That can't be!

246
00:16:11,542 --> 00:16:17,042
I'm sorry! I didn't mean to eavesdrop, but...!

247
00:16:17,042 --> 00:16:21,417
Ruka-<i>kun</i>. What message do
you want to send to the past?

248
00:16:21,417 --> 00:16:23,708
Well, actually...

249
00:16:25,125 --> 00:16:26,833
I want to be a girl!

250
00:16:26,833 --> 00:16:28,500
Huh?!

251
00:16:30,083 --> 00:16:34,333
I don't like the way I look...

252
00:16:34,333 --> 00:16:38,583
I've always felt that I might
feel more confident with myself

253
00:16:38,583 --> 00:16:41,292
if I were a girl...

254
00:16:41,292 --> 00:16:44,917
H-Hold on!

255
00:16:44,917 --> 00:16:48,708
What on earth is she talking about?

256
00:16:48,708 --> 00:16:53,625
Assistant. It appears
you've made a crucial mistake.

257
00:16:53,625 --> 00:16:55,167
A mistake?

258
00:16:55,167 --> 00:16:58,083
Rukako isn't a girl. He's a guy.

259
00:16:58,083 --> 00:17:00,417
What kind of joke is that?

260
00:17:00,417 --> 00:17:01,958
How short-sighted.

261
00:17:01,958 --> 00:17:06,625
If you're a real scientist,
then observe for yourself.

262
00:17:10,417 --> 00:17:14,833
Someone this cute
can't possibly be a boy...

263
00:17:14,833 --> 00:17:16,875
Sorry, I hope you don't mind.

264
00:17:23,375 --> 00:17:25,375
Are you okay?

265
00:17:25,375 --> 00:17:29,958
I'm serious about this!
I really want to be a girl!

266
00:17:29,958 --> 00:17:31,458
Please!

267
