Still, I'm not sure sending a
D-mail can change your gender.

268
00:17:37,500 --> 00:17:41,833
I've heard that if you eat lots
of meat while you're pregnant,

269
00:17:41,833 --> 00:17:43,833
you'll have a baby boy.

270
00:17:43,833 --> 00:17:48,667
And that if you eat lots of
vegetables instead, it'll be a girl.

271
00:17:48,667 --> 00:17:52,667
