331
00:21:17,917 --> 00:21:20,333
Yeah! It's cute!

332
00:21:20,333 --> 00:21:23,250
I think it'd look
wonderful on you, Ruka-<i>chan</i>!

333
00:21:23,250 --> 00:21:25,583
