343
00:21:49,000 --> 00:21:52,625
What kind of perverted thoughts
are you having, grinning like that?!

344
00:21:52,625 --> 00:21:54,083
Sheesh, Okarin!

345
00:21:54,083 --> 00:21:58,292
Honestly, now! You two
